assets/ — README screenshots
============================

v1.2.3 round-13 (2026.7.16) — README.license created:
  - This file documents the license classification for the root-level
    `assets/` directory, which contains screenshots referenced by README.md.
    Created for completeness — previously this directory had no
    README.license, unlike the 7 other directories (src/main, src/main/assets,
    src/main/assets/chess.src, src/main/cpp, src/main/java/com/Regalia,
    src/main/res, Manual) that each have one.
  - Version: versionCode=123, versionName="1.2.3" (unchanged — bug-fix round).
  - Files:
    * screenshot.jpg (AGPL v3): Gameplay screenshot shown at the top of
      README.md. Original work of the Regalia project.
    * screenshot.png (AGPL v3): Same screenshot in PNG format as a fallback
      for environments that don't render JPG inline. Original work.
  - License classification: both files are AGPL v3 (original works of the
    Regalia project). They are NOT packaged into the APK — they exist solely
    for README.md display on GitHub/F-Droid/source code browsers.
  - AI-GEN: AI assisted — this README.license was AI-assisted and has been
    reviewed for AGPL v3 compliance.
